    </p>

    <div class="instructions">
      <h2>Using the Chatbot</h2>
      <p>To chat with the AI, simply type your message in the input box at the bottom of the page and press "Send". You can also press the "Enter" key to send the message.</p>
      <p>The AI will respond to your queries based on the message you type. Try asking questions like:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>"Hello" or "Hi"</li>
        <li>"How are you?"</li>
        <li>"Help"</li>
      </ul>
      <p>If the AI doesn't understand your question, it will try to guide you with a response like "I'm not sure how to respond to that."</p>

      <h2>Konami Code</h2>
      <p>To activate the Konami Code, press the following sequence of keys on your keyboard:</p>
      <p><strong>Up, Up, Down, Down, Left, Right, Left, Right, B, A</strong></p>
      <p>Once the sequence is entered correctly, the page background will turn red, and a surprise message will appear in the chatbox.</p>
      <p>If you encounter any issues or need further assistance, feel free to reach out or restart the page.</p>

      <p>Click <a href="chatbox.html">here</a> to return to the chatbot.</p>
    </div>
